Ligero nearly crashed into his house but he managed to stick the landing “we are, uh, here!” Ligero huffed as his wings falpped a few last time

@Radioactive Lain
Quartz screamed when he almost crashed, but sighed out of relief *"Great !"* she tried to jump down
Ligero set her down and walked towards his door

She was still shaken up by the landing, and almost fell down.
"Damn, that was.... ***Awsome!!!***"
Ligero chuckled “that was the first time i’ve ever properly landed” he smiled as he struggled with unlocking his door
"wow really ? good job!" she giggled "uuuh, need some help with that door?"
“Oh, um, no, i’m fine!” He passed off, but it took him a tad bit more before he just distorted his bodyand went threw under neath the door, he then unlocked it from the inside “well, come on in!”
"Ok ! " she smiled and walked through the door happily
Ligero chuckled and closed the door “ what-ya wanna eat, kid?” He asked
She looked around, jumping on anything she could "Uuuuuh... Pasta, I haven't eaten that in a while !"

Logero nodded and then went into the kitchen, 

(Time skip, becuase me not know the ways of pasta
Quartz was laying on a couch, like a cat, and was napping

Ligero was on the back of a chair watching the pasta cook, 

(I know little in the ways of pasta, but i;d be damned if kars wasn’t a freak while waiting for food to cook_)
She started to snore loudly, she was very tired
Ligero perked up and jumped off the chair he waled to the living room to see quartz sleeping, he sighed shaking his head before getting a blanket and draping it over quartz
she rolled herself up in the blanket and muttered a small "thank you"
Ligero chukled patted quartz head and went back to the pasta
Alright now timeskip? Cuase we can’t be having a real time event of makeing -asta)
Pasta*
((Yeah
Quartz woke up, and walked to the kitchen
Ligero was hopping around with his chair (like hes on the back and is schooching around) while putting the pasta and-a meatballs on plates “foods ready, theres drinks in the fridge” ligero said
She yawned and streched "oh, sweet ! looking delicious!" she lazily opened the fridge to take some water before sitting at the table
Ligero attempted to scooch to the fridge on his chairmobile but fell and slammed his face agasint the floor
Quartz tried to not burst out laughing but miserably failed and laughed hysterically at the situation, falling off of her chair
Ligero flopped around trying to get up
Quartz kept laughing for a bit, before getting up, cackling like an idiot "Need any help ?"
Ligero huffed “maybe” he mumbled both his legs had somehow gotten tangled in the chair

She kept herself from laughing again, putting her hand on her mouth and mumbling "Ok, I'll help" 
She took a deep breath to calm down, and tried to untangle Ligero's legs

Ligero tried struggling out of the chair but was not helping the situation 

“I can;t die like this...”
She sighed "I'm sorry for what I'm about to do, birdman, but that's the only option left..." She punched as hard as she could the chair and broke it, freeing Ligero's legs
Ligero cried “chaaaaairmobiiile!”
She took a dramatic tone, clenching her fist "It had to be done, you'll be missed, soldier"
Ligero sat up and in the most dramatic way “CHAAAAAAAAAIR-ZAAAAAA”
She patted his back, a single tear in her eyes "His sacrifice will not be forgotten"
Ligero nodded before standing “anyways, we do need to clean this up” he sighed
"Yeah, you're right, we should" she started to pick up some of the pieces
Ligero also began to grab the pieces, humming his own theme
"Where do I put them ?" she asked, her arms full of broken pieces of the chair
Ligero pointed to a trash can by the counter, it was quite large, so it should hold everything
"ok !" she walked happily to the trash can and dropped  in everything before picking up pieces again
Ligero did the same
Riveting story)
As soon as she was done, she jumped back on her chair and started to eat
Ligero also satat the table after grabbing a mountain dew from the fridge
she smirked and decided to catapult with her fork a piece of meatball towards Ligero's drink
Ligero grabbed the meatball quickly before eating it “thank you for some extra food, dear” ligero chuckled and he took a sip of mt. Dew

she stared, shocked, mouth wide open *damn that was fast* she thought, but she wasn't giving up 
she tried again, but this time, she turned the meat invisible
Ligero used his scent and managed to catch it again, although barely “nice try kid” he smirked and chuckled, before grabbing a small peice of his own meatball and sending it barreling towards quartz
She managed to conter it with her fork, sending it back to Ligero
Ligero ate it as it went towards him,
Quartz pouted, and decided to go all out, and picked a bunch of meat, turned it invisible, and sent them all at the same time towards Ligero
Ligero managed to grab some, but the rest hit, he stood and with his long arm slammed his hand against quartz face he then got more food with his other head and threw it at quartz “hah!”
*"Hey ! Cheater !!"* she struggled, trying to get his hand off her face and pushing away the food, she tried to bite one of Ligero's fingers
Ligero jerked away he slipped and slammed agaisnt the floor
She stared at him, and got up "Oh shit, you're ok ??!"
Ligero shot up grabbed quartz plate and threw the food at her “mwahaaha, see! You can’t even beat me in a game of food fight! It shows, that i am the superior being” he boomed out a luagh

She stood there, silent, feeling betrayed, food all over her face.
***"Oh, I see"*** she took as much food as she could, and she turned herself invisible. She grabbed Ligero's drink, and started to run in circle around him at high speed, throwing everything she had at him
Ligero was overwhelmed by this and rose his arms in defense, he began to quickly grab out around himself to catch quartz

Quartz was fast and at a safe distance, so she managed to avoid Ligero, although he was very close to catching her.
Once all the food was thrown, she threw the rest of Ligero's drink before climbing on the fridge and turning visible again, smirking
Ligero looked at his spilled drink, and then saw that his socks were soggy, he began shaking, his wings slowly unfolding he growled “you’ll pay! “ he cried as he barrelled towards the fridge
***"OH SHIT"*** as soon as she saw the mun unfolding his wings, she jumped of the fridge and ran to the living room as fast as she could, jumping over every obstacles.
Ligero bolts after quartz at an ungodly speed,
Quartz ended up turning herself invisible trying to hide from him
Ligero smelled the air, and did ran towards the scent of the person, although he was inacurate he spread his wings so he could feel her out or knock her off guard
she rolled on the floor, trying to avoid the wings, and attempted to open the door without making a noise
(Ligero has a sofa which one probably can’t get under)
Ligero whipped around he barreled to quartz his wings spread out wide
She let out a scream, raising her arms to protect herself
Ligero grabbed quartz and made a dome around them with his wings, “now your trapped with me” he said
she moved her tail and the cristal scratched Ligero's wings, and she hissed
Ligero didn’t react to the pain and continued gripping quartzes shoulders tightly,
"Let me go!" she struggled trying to escape
Ligero slowly started to embrace quartz “you are trapped with me” he mumbled
Quartz looked at him, now more confused than anything "Could you let me go?"
Ligero set quartz down and let go back away a bit his wings furled back in
she smirked ***"so, I won the food fight-"***
Ligero frowned before whipping out her plate of spaghet and pushing it in her face “of course not” he smiled,
She licked the plate after pushing it away from her face *"Buuuut I did pretty Good, didn't I ?"*
Ligero luaghed and nodded “pretty good kiddo, but it seems, not good enough” he smirked before stretching and flicking some food out of his hair
"Give me a break, urg !" She closed her eyes and put her arms in front of her face to try and stop the food
Ligero chuckled and set down the plate, he returned to. Neutral state “what a mess” he mumbled before sighing
She cackled "But it was fun !" She got up and stretched "Let's get this house cleaned !"

Ligero nodded “you can pick up the chunks i’ll go get the mop” ligero said before trotting up stairs you could see the urge to run up them like a dog was strong in his as he slouched but regained his good posture again

"Alright Li'!" 
She let out a slight chukle before picking up the food on the floor
Ligero walked down his hallway trying to find the closet, when he did, a shit load of mops and brooms and shit fell on him

Quartz started to laugh, falling on the ground holding her stomach.
***"What of Cartoonish shit is this OH MY GOD"***
Ligero struggled up and grabbed a broom and stuff, he then came back to quartz a mop on his head
Quartz was still losing it on the floor after seeing the mop on Ligero's head. She was crying out of laughter
Ligero huffed and chuckled, before handing quartz a mop and mop
Buckey*
Bucket*

She took the mop and bucket and started to clean, humming a song.
She even started to dance a little as she was mopping
Ligero chuckled as he began to work on the kitchen he hummed along to quartzes humming
She was mopping the living room in style, singing and dancing, getting a little carried away

She dropped the mop
"Sorry, I gotta go, see ya dude !" She jumped through the window
Ligero was quite confused but waved “bye?”
